title: Paris Underground (1945 - USA) WWII invasion drama
description:
Paris Underground (1945 - USA) aka Madame Pimpernel

Drama / War
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0037972/


Academy Awards - NOMINATED - Best Music

An American and an Englishwoman, both stranded in France after the Nazi invasion, help RAF pilots to escape. They are arrested and tortured but saved by the liberation. The screenplay was based on the true wartime activities of Etta Shiber, who engineered the escape of nearly 300 Allied pilots.
